OL,3,C'They just took the baby away': Family
OL,4,Cspeaks out in church-run homes scandal
OL,6,FA family has come forward following an
OL,7,FITV News investigation into cruelty
OL,8,Fand abuse at ex church run mother and
OL,9,Fbaby homes, Social Affairs
OL,10,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker reports
OL,12,FFurther allegations of abuse and
OL,13,Fneglect at a former church-run mother
OL,14,Fand baby home in Cumbria have emerged,
OL,15,Ffollowing an ITV News investigation.
OL,17,FEarlier this year we revealed that 45
OL,18,Fbabies who had died at St Monica's
OL,19,Fhome - in Kendal were buried in an
OL,20,Funmarked grave in the town's cemetery.
