OL,3,C'They just took the baby away': Family
OL,4,Cspeaks out in church-run homes scandal
OL,6,FSt Monica's was one of hundreds of
OL,7,Fhomes for unmarried mothers across
OL,8,FEngland.
OL,10,FBetween 1949 and the mid-1970s, an
OL,11,Festimated 200,000 women were sent away
OL,12,Fto homes run by churches and the state
OL,13,Fwhere they were pressured and coerced
OL,14,Fin to give up their babies for
OL,15,Fadoption. Other infants died through
OL,16,Fpoor care.
