OL,3,C'They just took the baby away': Family
OL,4,Cspeaks out in church-run homes scandal
OL,6,FSince our first report aired in July,
OL,7,Fthe family of one of those children
OL,8,Fhas come forward and told ITV News
OL,9,Fthat their mother was lied to about
OL,10,Fthe fate of her baby daughter, Faith,
OL,11,Fand was never told where she was
OL,12,Fburied.
OL,14,FNorah Everard was in her 80s, and
OL,15,Fdying from cancer, when she told her
OL,16,Ffamily for the first time about the
OL,17,Ftrauma she'd endured decades earlier
OL,18,Fas a teenager in 1941.
