OL,6,FPregnant and unmarried, she was sent
OL,7,Faway to St Monica's, which was run by
OL,8,Fthe Diocese of Carlisle, to have her
OL,9,Fbaby.
OL,11,FNorah's son Bob Chubb recounted the
OL,12,Fdetails that his late mother shared
OL,13,Fwith him and his wife Carole about the
OL,14,F"cruel" home.
