OL,6,F"We were all round the table one
OL,7,FChristmas, and she said 'I've got
OL,8,Fsomething important to tell you both.
OL,9,FBob you weren't my first born', and
OL,10,Fthen she told me about being raped as
OL,11,Fa young school girl, going to St
OL,12,FMonica's in Kendal to have the baby,
OL,13,Fand the baby was stillborn, called
OL,14,FFaith," Bob told ITV News.
