OL,3,C'They just took the baby away': Family
OL,4,Cspeaks out in church-run homes scandal
OL,6,FBurial records seen by ITV News
OL,7,Fsuggest that Norah was lied to, they
OL,8,Fshow that Faith wasn't stillborn and
OL,9,Fthat she had lived for 12 hours and
OL,10,Fwas later buried in an unmarked grave
OL,11,Fat Parkside Cemetery in Kendal - one
OL,12,Fof the 45 babies who were buried in
OL,13,Fsecrecy.
OL,15,F"I don't think she was told the truth.
OL,16,FI think some terrible things went on,"
OL,17,FMr Chubb said.
