OL,4,Cspeaks out in church-run homes scandal
OL,6,FCarole Chubb, Bob's wife, said: "It
OL,7,Freally really disgusts me. They just
OL,8,Ftook the baby away and said the baby's
OL,9,Fdead and that's it. Did they even
OL,10,Fgiven her any milk? Would she have
OL,11,Fsurvived?
OL,13,F"Norah told me it was cruel place,
OL,14,Fthey made the women scrub floors when
OL,15,Fthey were heavily pregnant and they
OL,16,Fwere refused pain relief in labour as
OL,17,Fa punishment."
OL,19,FBob and Carole share his mother
OL,20,FNorah's story with ITV News
