OL,6,F"The Church of England should do all
OL,7,Fit can to support people who have
OL,8,Flived with the trauma. We need to
OL,9,Flisten and give them a choice in
OL,10,Fdecision making so they can tell us
OL,11,Fwhat they need and as an organisation
OL,12,Fwe show them the love and dignity that
OL,13,Fthey weren't shown before," he said.
OL,15,FThe family of another baby, Stephen
