OL,4,Cspeaks out in church-run homes scandal
OL,6,FIt was years later when baby Stephen's
OL,7,Fmother Judith Hindley first told her
OL,8,Fhusband, also called Stephen, of the
OL,9,Fabuse she endured at the 'draconian'
OL,10,Fhome in the late 1960s.
OL,12,F"Judith was 17 at the time and told me
OL,13,Fhow she was forced to clean floors and
OL,14,Fkitchens while heavily pregnant. They
OL,15,Fwere being punished," he said.
OL,17,F"Her son Stephen was born with
OL,18,Fdisabilities and needed to go to
OL,19,Fhospital, but he was cruelly denied
OL,20,Fproper medical care and died 11 weeks
OL,21,Flater."
